EMS training data set 2010-2016

Number of epidemic disasters per country per year that were reported to the WHO between 2010-2016.

data(emstrain)

Format

An object of class "data.table".

Examples

data(emstrain)
#> Warning: data set ‘emstrain’ not found
str(train)
